it mention of using browser developer tools, the console, and network requests for debugging as a specific skill, though it is highly probable given their experience.', \"There is no explicit mention of Power BI experience. However, the requirement is 'server-side tracking AND/OR Power BI', and server-side tracking experience is present.\", 'There is no explicit statement about living in Germany, though the candidate mentions attending Berlin-based events and working in Germany for various companies, which strongly suggests this is the case.'], 'bonus': ['Candidate has experience rebuilding an entire Analytics department from scratch, demonstrating strong leadership and foundational skills.', 'Experience with predictive analytics initiatives is a bonus.', 'Experience with AI chatbots and developing own AI agents showcases advanced technical curiosity and skills.', \"Previous experience in a consulting role (Company 3) aligns with the candidate's interest in a consulting or agency role.\", 'Speaking engagements at industry events.'], 'summary': 'The candidate is a highly experienced Digital Analytics expert with extensive GA4, GTM, and Looker Studio skills, privacy-compliant tracking implementation, and significant experience across various marketing channels, making them a very strong match for the Digital Analytics / Web Tracking Expert role.'}"}
