ools beyond GA4, such as eTracker and Webtrekk, indicating broader expertise.', 'Experience in building predictive analytics initiatives.', 'Practical experience with AI chatbots and developing own AI agents, which could enhance analytical capabilities and efficiency.', 'Active participation in the professional community, including attending industry conferences and volunteering, showcasing continuous learning and engagement.', 'Experience with GraphQL, which may be beneficial for advanced data integrations.'], 'summary': 'The candidate is a strong match for the Digital Analytics / Web Tracking Expert role, possessing extensive experience with GA4, GTM, and CMPs, a technical understanding of tracking implementations including JavaScript and server-side tracking, and strong dashboarding skills in Looker Studio, with fluent German and professional English.'}"}
